      "question_fr": "Le nombre complexe $\\left(\\frac{5-3i}{3+5i}\\right)^{2025}$ est égal à :",
      "choices": [
        {
          "label": "A",
          "fr": "$i$"
        },
        {
          "label": "B",
          "fr": "$-i$"
        },
        {
          "label": "C",
          "fr": "$1$"
        },
        {
          "label": "D",
          "fr": "$3+5i$"
        }
      ],
      "correctIndex": 1,
      "explanation_fr": "$5-3i = -i(3+5i)$ donc $\\frac{5-3i}{3+5i} = -i$. Alors $(-i)^{2025}=(-i)^{2024}\\cdot(-i)=1\\cdot(-i)=-i$."
    },
